Data

Well investigate the credit dataset from the textbook, which has 400 observations on customers financial information.

The aim of the dataset is to predict which customers will default on their credit card debt.

Model Fit

Model \(R^2\) Adjusted \(R^2\)
Credit Limit 0.745 0.811
Credit Limit + Student 0.812 0.811


How much additional variability in debt can we explain when adding in whether the individual was a student?
